	 Peru - Package - MACHU PICCHU 
	 High on jungle-covered hilltops, Machu Picchu was never found by the Spanish conquerors and many parts of the ancient city remain to be discovered. Energetic visitors can climb the heights of the nearby Huayna Picchu for fine photographs of the archaeological wonder and surrounding countryside. The even more energetic can hike the four-day Inca Trail connecting Cuzco with Machu Picchu. 
